{"tid":167995,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿「銷毁」圖書館簡體字書藉被控盜竊罪　押後至4月再訊","createTime":"2017-03-23T08:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T01:23:25.000Z","uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed40f1a7d26df790fdf80b8ae5e625178c95a0ae","tid":167995,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"綽號「四眼哥哥」的熱血公民副主席鄭錦滿，去年在社交網站上載短片、聲稱要教網民「銷毁」公共圖書館的簡體字書藉，片中有人在圖書館將多本簡體字書丟進垃圾桶。鄭錦滿被控一項盜竊罪，今早於九龍城裁判院提堂，鄭暫時無須答辯，案件押後至4月20日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告鄭錦滿（28歲）涉於去年3月29日在九龍公共圖書館4樓偷竊9本圖書。辯方申請押後案件，以索取文件及法律意見，期間鄭獲准以500元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n我們都是牙悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbd7aec3ae73b61d4ae73c6e1fa0ad18bdfb9de","tid":167995,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"盜竊罪咁嚴重典解都仲有得保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe31eea901868a2eb9ae84624b22fef9c0ac8e8a","tid":167995,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盜竊罪咁嚴重典解都仲有得保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為佢老細收左共產黨錢？"},{"pid":"679921f747c4553d52fa636d901bb6f7b51debca","tid":167995,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>盜竊罪咁嚴重典解都仲有得保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為佢老細收左共產黨錢？</blockquote><br />\n@何金水"},{"pid":"9a3ea89d94849ba72ea0cb8be87410c236ebfbd3","tid":167995,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"圖書館都ko到隻熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj